
jQuery formwizard is a jQuery plugin which turns a regular HTML form into a wizard with very little effort. The plugin supports AJAX form submission, form validation and browser back and forward buttons, all through integration with the following jQuery plugins: jQuery form, jQuery validation and the BBQ plugin.

The formwizard plugin source is located under /js/jquery.form.wizard-3.0.4.js

A bunch of examples that tries to highlight different use cases can be found in the /examples/ folder

The plugins official demo page can be found at http://thecodemine.org
